Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:07.46,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:14.75,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:22.93,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I closed my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:28.94,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,and distanced myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:35.70,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,5 PM in the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:42.58,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,The ball's shadow is growing tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:50.04,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.76,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:58.51,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,we always quarreled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:06.69,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:13.65,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:20.99,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I opened my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:27.79,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,and we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A lodge where even time seemed to freeze.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A girl named Emma Easton from\nMinato International School came,\nin search of the snowman legend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Following her arrival,\nstrange things began to occur.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time came to a halt and Emma\ndisappeared into a blizzard after\nbeing assaulted by two strange men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:01.11,eptitle,Title,0000,0350,0000,,{\pos(375,25)\c&H26258C&\2c&H273485&}Episode 10
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:01.11,eptitle,Title,0000,0350,0000,,{\pos(230,154)\c&H26258C&\2c&H273485&}Avalanche Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's hoping\nyou'd beat the snowman, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take that thing seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun having one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't grab my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw a snowman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I saw one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bummer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel it. It's near us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The jerks who trashed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them? Damn, they were tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had Emma's picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't taking me serious, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're after Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So am I !
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I don't wanna talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell that to Daijoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daijoji, stand in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you coming with me?\nI don't wanna go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh, it's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Busy, aren't ya?\nGet off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where Emma went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival... it has been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to cling on to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the dinner ticket\nat the new building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll throw in the special dinner show.\nMake that two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin, say aah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, when will you be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scream at me all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be faster if we teleport and get her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous.\nThose men are after Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mr. Snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad ! Dad !
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? You look scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It howled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snowman over there. It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to fool us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Tell me when the snowman starts walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you you'd pull our legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean pull your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuddup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. Those are Tomomi's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking a bath first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's chilly. Isn't the heater on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here. The hot water in the tub is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... it's frozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daijoji, let go of me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may call me Rumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I said, let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumi would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd get dizzy if you swirl that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worried about Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi loves Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister has very a strange taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the snowman's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Daijoji !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, you have to come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the fire going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire is burning in the furnace inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must keep the fire going here,\nor disaster will come. It has to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuguradoshirutoneriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to keep the fire going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old lady said we have to keep the fire\ngoing there, or something bad will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just superstition, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:11:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When grandma said {\i1}"yuguradoshirutoneriko"{\i0},\nthe sky lit as if it's responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why I felt dizzy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did grandma say again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,uh... yu... gu... yu... gu... yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuguradoshirutoneriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that some sort of spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll start by the peak of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The avalanche is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, where are you going?\nTomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, what's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NODA?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NOTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we'll send somebody right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still investigating the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when will the heater get fixed?\nI'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will make announcement on PA\nas soon as we find out the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What about my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, over there! I heard their voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me about the avalanche?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Emma, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?\nWhy are you after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, we're here to save you.\nLet's go back to the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the path of the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The path of the spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My prayer to the snowman\nand the white deer was heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure you don't want\nto report this to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to look into the matter before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find out anything, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me. They are good for nothing.\nI'll protect you all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'd like to know your\nphone number and measurements...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I see a bikini babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've met once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hijack incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again, miracle girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no bikini babe anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your phone number and measurements!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.\nWe'll be returning by plane tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:48.45,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0440,,Halfway through a kiss, Tears dropped out, Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:53.84,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0440,,Because I closed my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin, you're great !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, how is the ride on the bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're excavating an old grave mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grave mound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get excited\nabout tragic love in the ancient past?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls,\n"Watch Out for the Time Flow"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's crying in the mound !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:07.87,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:11.36,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.48,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:18.01,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:38.00,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:49.89,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:58.00,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:05.58,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.71,0:23:11.19,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:14.56,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:20.35,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:22.86,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:26.43,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:29.56,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:33.73,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
